00015 subroutine force_laser(p_start,p_finish)
00016 
00017   use physvars
00018   use treevars
00019   use utils
00020   implicit none
00021   include 'mpif.h'
00022 
00023   integer, intent(in) :: p_start,p_finish  ! min, max particle nos.
00024   integer :: p
00025   real :: xd, yd, zd  ! positions relative to centre of laser spot
00026   real :: xt, yt, zt, rt  ! positions relative to plasma centre
00027   real :: Epon_x, Epon_y, Epon_z, Phipon, ex_em, ey_em, ez_em, bx_em, by_em, bz_em, az_em
00028 
00029   if (itime>0 .and. beam_config==4) focus(1) = x_crit  ! laser tracks n_c
00030 
00031   ! Include force from laser/external field on electrons - ES scheme
00032 
00033   if (beam_config >= 3 .and. beam_config <=7 ) then
00034      do p = p_start, p_finish
00035         if (q(p)<0) then
00036            xd = x(p)-focus(1)
00037            yd = y(p)-focus(2)
00038            zd = z(p)-focus(3)
00039 
00040            laser_model: select case(beam_config_in)
00041 
00042            case(3)  ! Uniform sinusoid in x (s-pol)
00043               Epon_z = 0.
00044               Epon_y = 0.
00045               Epon_x = vosc*omega*sin(omega*tlaser)
00046               Bx_em = 0.
00047               By_em = 0.
00048               Bz_em = 0.
00049 
00050            case(23)  ! Uniform sinusoid in z (s-pol)
00051               Epon_x = 0.
00052               Epon_y = 0.
00053               Epon_z = vosc*omega*sin(omega*tlaser)
00054               Bx_em = 0.
00055               By_em = 0.
00056               Bz_em = 0.
00057 
00058 
00059            case(4)  ! standing wave fpond, sin2 pulse
00060               call fpond( tlaser, tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega,rho_upper, &
00061                    xd,yd,zd,epon_x,epon_y,epon_z,phipon)
00062               Bx_em = 0.
00063               By_em = 0.
00064               Bz_em = 0.
00065 
00066            case(14)  ! standing wave fpond, linear rise-time, fields reduced
00067               call fpond_lin( tlaser, tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega,rho_upper, &
00068                    xd,yd,zd,epon_x,epon_y,epon_z,phipon)
00069               epon_y=epon_y/50.
00070               epon_z=epon_z/50.
00071               Bx_em = 0.
00072               By_em = 0.
00073               Bz_em = 0.
00074 
00075            case(94)  ! standing wave fpond with transverse fields artificially reduced
00076               call fpond( tlaser, tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega,rho_upper, &
00077                    xd,yd,zd,epon_x,epon_y,epon_z,phipon)
00078               epon_y=epon_y/10.
00079               epon_z=epon_z/10.
00080               Bx_em = 0.
00081               By_em = 0.
00082               Bz_em = 0.
00083 
00084            case(24)  ! oblique incidence standing wave, s-pol
00085               call emobliq( tlaser, tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega,theta_beam,rho_upper, &
00086                    xd,yd,zd,epon_x,epon_y,epon_z,phipon,ez_em,bx_em,by_em)
00087               Bz_em = 0.
00088 
00089            case(34) ! fpond with fully EM components Gaussian spot, sin^2 pulse
00090               call empond(tlaser,tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega,xd,yd,zd,Epon_z,By_em,Bx_em,az_em,phipon)
00091               Epon_x=0.
00092               Epon_y=0.
00093               Bz_em=0.
00094 
00095            case(5)  ! propagating fpond
00096               call laser_bullet( tlaser, focus(1), tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega, & 
00097                    xd,yd,zd,epon_x,epon_y,epon_z,phipon)
00098               Bx_em = 0.
00099               By_em = 0.
00100               Bz_em = 0.
00101 
00102            case(6) ! plane wave with Gaussian spot, sin^2 pulse
00103               call emplane(tlaser,tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega,xd,yd,zd,Epon_z,By_em,Bx_em,az_em,phipon)
00104               Epon_x=0.
00105               Epon_y=0.
00106               Bz_em=0.
00107 
00108            case(16) ! plane wave with Gaussian spot, linear rise-time
00109               call emplane_lin(tlaser,tpulse,sigma,vosc,omega,xd,yd,zd,Epon_z,By_em,Bx_em,az_em,phipon)
00110               Epon_x=0.
00111               Epon_y=0.
00112               Bz_em=0.
00113 
00114            case default  ! no laser
00115               Epon_x=0
00116               Epon_y=0
00117               Epon_z=0
00118               Bx_em = 0.
00119               By_em = 0.
00120               Bz_em = 0.
00121 
00122            end select laser_model
00123 
00124         else    ! (q>0)
00125            !  ions assumed not to feel laser, so zero fields
00126            Epon_x=0
00127            Epon_y=0
00128            Epon_z=0
00129            Bx_em = 0.
00130            By_em = 0.
00131            Bz_em = 0.
00132 
00133         endif
00134 
00135         if (beam_config_in==7)  then ! Constant B in z-direction - either charge
00136            Epon_x=0.
00137            Epon_y=0.
00138            Epon_z=0.
00139            Bx_em = 0.
00140            By_em = 0.
00141            Bz_em = vosc
00142 
00143         else if (beam_config_in==17)  then !  Z-pinch: circular B in x,y
00144            xt=x(p) - plasma_centre(1)
00145            yt=y(p) - plasma_centre(2)
00146            zt=z(p) - plasma_centre(3)
00147            rt = sqrt(xt**2+yt**2)
00148            Epon_x=0.
00149            Epon_y=0.
00150            Epon_z=0.
00151            Bx_em = -vosc*yt/rt
00152            By_em = vosc*xt/rt
00153            Bz_em = 0.
00154 
00155         else if (beam_config_in==27)  then !  Tokamak: circular B in theta + const Bz
00156            xt=x(p) - plasma_centre(1)
00157            yt=y(p) - plasma_centre(2)
00158            zt=z(p) - plasma_centre(3)
00159            rt = sqrt(xt**2+yt**2)
00160            Epon_x=0.
00161            Epon_y=0.
00162            Epon_z=0.
00163            Bx_em = -vosc/3.*yt/rt
00164            By_em = vosc/3.*xt/rt
00165            Bz_em = vosc
00166 
00167         else if (beam_config_in==37)  then !  Mirror in Bz
00168            xt=x(p) - plasma_centre(1)
00169            yt=y(p) - plasma_centre(2)
00170            zt=z(p) - plasma_centre(3)
00171            rt = sqrt(xt**2+yt**2)
00172            Epon_x=0.
00173            Epon_y=0.
00174            Epon_z=0.          
00175            Bx_em = 0.
00176            By_em = 0.
00177     
00178            if (zt>-zl/2. .and. zt<zl/2.) then
00179               Bx_em = -vosc/5.*xt/rt*(2*zt/zl)
00180               By_em = -vosc/5.*yt/rt*(2*zt/zl)
00181 
00182               Bz_em = vosc*(2*zt/zl)**2+vosc/5.
00183            else
00184               Bx_em=0.
00185               By_em=0.
00186               Bz_em = 0.
00187            endif
00188         endif
00189 
00190         ! Add external fields to new particle field
00191         Ex(p) = Ex(p) + Epon_x
00192         Ey(p) = Ey(p) + Epon_y
00193         Ez(p) = Ez(p) + Epon_z
00194         Bx(p) = Bx(p) + Bx_em
00195         By(p) = By(p) + By_em
00196         Bz(p) = Bz(p) + Bz_em
00197 
00198      end do
00199   endif
00200 
00201 end subroutine force_laser
